{"hierarchy":{"paths":[[]]},"kind":"symbol","topicSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton"],"title":"Group","anchor":"Group"},{"generated":true,"anchor":"Enumerations","title":"Enumerations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/AccessibilityFocusable"]},{"title":"Extended Modules","identifiers":["doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/SwiftUICore"],"anchor":"Extended-Modules","generated":true}],"sections":[],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"module","role":"collection","modules":[{"name":"OUDSComponents"}],"title":"OUDSComponents","roleHeading":"Framework","externalID":"OUDSComponents"},"abstract":[{"text":"The catalog of all components provided by OUDS. It contains also ","type":"text"},{"code":"View","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" extensions and ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ViewModifiers"},{"text":" to apply tokens and styles on components and higher-level views.","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"text":"Overview","anchor":"Overview","type":"heading","level":2},{"text":"Buttons","type":"heading","anchor":"Buttons","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton"},{"text":" propose layout with text only, icon only or text and icon.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Four hierarchies are proposed for all layouts: "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"strong"}]},{"text":", ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"minimal"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"negative","type":"text"}]},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"Two style are available: "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" and ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"loading"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"If button is placed on colored surface using ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSColoredSurface","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":", the default colors (content, background and border) are automatically adjusted to switch to monochrom."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"A button with ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSButton.Hierarchy.Negative","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" hierarchy is not allowed as a direct or indirect child of an "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSColoredSurface"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","code":["     \/\/ Icon only with default hierarchy","     OUDSButton(hierarchy: .default, icon: Image(\"ic_heart\")) {}","","     \/\/ Text only with negative hierarchy","     OUDSButton(hierarchy: .negative, text: \"Delete\") {}","","     \/\/ Text and icon with strong hierarchy","     OUDSButton(hierarchy: .strong, icon: Image(\"ic_heart\"), text: \"Validate\") {}"],"syntax":"swift"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Customize-components","text":"Customize components","level":2},{"level":3,"type":"heading","text":"Apply a specific shadow effect (elevation tokens)","anchor":"Apply-a-specific-shadow-effect-elevation-tokens"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The unified design system implemented by OUDS iOS library allows to apply "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"elevation effets","type":"text"}]},{"text":" on a ","type":"text"},{"code":"View","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", i.e. a shadow under the component.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Because the design tool in use is ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Figma","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" which defines such shadow with a "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"blur","type":"text"}]},{"text":" and a ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"spread"}]},{"text":" radiuses, and because ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"SwiftUI"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" uses only its own "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"radius","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" definition, an extension of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"View"},{"type":"text","text":" has been implemented to let users apply some effect using an "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/oudstokenssemantic\/elevationcompositesemantictoken","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" from the "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/oudstokenssemantic\/","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" library thanks to the method ","type":"text"},{"code":"shadow(elevation: ElevationCompositeSemanticToken)","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ For example, apply the elevation effect \"elevationDragLight\" from your theme:","myView.shadow(elevation: theme.elevationDragLight)","","\/\/ And in the theme this \"elevationDragLight\" has been defined for example like:","@objc open var elevationDragLight: ElevationCompositeSemanticToken { ElevationRawTokens.elevationBottom_3_500 }","ColorRawTokens.colorOpacityBlack400)","","\/\/ And if you look deeper, the raw token \"elevationBottom_3_500\" can be like:","public static let elevationBottom_3_500 = ElevationCompositeRawToken(x: 0, y: 4, blur: 4, color: ColorRawTokens.colorOpacityBlack500)","","\/\/ Blur will be used to compute the radius value"]},{"level":3,"anchor":"Apply-a-specific-typography-font-tokens","type":"heading","text":"Apply a specific typography (font tokens)"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Your application identity can be strongly based on the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"typography","type":"text"}]},{"text":" you use, i.e. the font family you choose and other configuration details like the font size or the font weight.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"With OUDS, typography depends to the class size, i.e. wether or not the application is in ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"compact mode"}]},{"type":"text","text":" or in "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"regular mode"}]},{"text":", and is defined with a ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/oudstokenssemantic\/multiplefontcompositerawtokens","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":". defined in the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/oudstokenssemantic\/fontsemantictokens\/"},{"type":"text","text":"."}]},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"theme","type":"text"}]},{"text":" contains lots of ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens"},{"text":" listing all the combinations of typography you can apply, and these ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"composite semantic tokens"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" use "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"composite raw tokens"}]},{"type":"text","text":". For example:"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Here is a definition of a semantic token inside the theme for typography \"typeDisplayMedium\":","@objc open var typeDisplayMedium: MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens { ","MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens(compact: FontRawTokens.typeBold750, regular: FontRawTokens.typeBold1050) ","}","","\/\/ And here are the raw tokebs definitions:","public static let typeBold750 = FontCompositeRawToken(size: fontSize750, lineHeight: fontLineHeight850, weight: fontWeightBold)","","public static let typeBold1050 = FontCompositeRawToken(size: fontSize1050, lineHeight: fontLineHeight1150, weight: fontWeightBold)"]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"However the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"theme","type":"text"}]},{"text":" must know which ","type":"text"},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"font family"}]},{"text":" to apply, and this font family can be a ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"custom one"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" or the "},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"system one","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Thus, we let the users define the font family they want by overriding the ","type":"text"},{"code":"fontFamily","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" property. This value will be used to compute the typography, if not defined the systme font will be used.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Thus, if you want to apply a specific typography to a ","type":"text"},{"code":"View","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":", supposing you defined previously the semantic tokens, just call the method you want and gives as parameter the theme (to get the custom font if defined):","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["\/\/ Apply typography \"type body default small\"","myView.typeBodyDefaultSmall(theme)","","\/\/ Apply typography \"type label strong X large\"","myView.typeLabelStrongXLarge(theme)","","\/\/ Etc."]},{"anchor":"Apply-a-specific-border-border-tokens","type":"heading","level":3,"text":"Apply a specific border (border tokens)"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This module exposes the helper "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"oudsBorder(style:width:radius:color)"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to apply border semantic tokens on a view in order to define a border effect."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The helper is available through "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"View"},{"type":"text","text":", and tokens through the provider of the theme."}]},{"code":["    @Environment(\\.theme) private var theme","","    var body: some View {","        SomeView()","        .oudsBorder(","             style: theme.borders.borderStyleDefault,","             width: theme.borders.borderWidthThin,","             radius: theme.borders.borderRadiusNone,","             color: theme.colors.colorBorderDefault)","     }"],"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift"}],"kind":"content"}],"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"references":{"doc://ouds-ios.OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/SwiftUICore":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/swiftuicore","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/SwiftUICore","title":"SwiftUICore","role":"collection","abstract":[],"kind":"symbol"},"https://ios.unified-design-system.orange.com/documentation/oudstokenssemantic/fontsemantictokens/":{"type":"link","title":"OUDSTkensSemantic FontSemanticTokens","url":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/oudstokenssemantic\/fontsemantictokens\/","titleInlineContent":[{"code":"OUDSTkensSemantic","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"FontSemanticTokens"}],"identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/oudstokenssemantic\/fontsemantictokens\/"},"doc://ouds-ios.OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents","title":"OUDSComponents","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The catalog of all components provided by OUDS. It contains also "},{"code":"View","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" extensions and "},{"code":"ViewModifiers","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" to apply tokens and styles on components and higher-level views."}],"role":"collection"},"doc://ouds-ios.OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/AccessibilityFocusable":{"type":"topic","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/accessibilityfocusable","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/AccessibilityFocusable","title":"AccessibilityFocusable","abstract":[{"text":"Value to use as a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AccessibilityFocusState"},{"text":" to request focus.","type":"text"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"AccessibilityFocusable","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"enum","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"AccessibilityFocusable","kind":"identifier"}]},"https://ios.unified-design-system.orange.com/documentation/oudstokenssemantic/":{"identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/oudstokenssemantic\/","titleInlineContent":[{"text":"OUDSTokensSemantic","type":"text"}],"type":"link","title":"OUDSTokensSemantic","url":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/oudstokenssemantic\/"},"https://ios.unified-design-system.orange.com/documentation/oudstokenssemantic/multiplefontcompositerawtokens":{"type":"link","title":"MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens","url":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/oudstokenssemantic\/multiplefontcompositerawtokens","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"MultipleFontCompositeRawTokens"}],"identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/oudstokenssemantic\/multiplefontcompositerawtokens"},"doc://ouds-ios.OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSButton":{"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsbutton","identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSButton"}],"type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ouds-ios.OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSButton","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" proposes layout with text only, icon only or text with icon.","type":"text"}],"kind":"symbol","title":"OUDSButton","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSButton"}]},"https://ios.unified-design-system.orange.com/documentation/oudstokenssemantic/elevationcompositesemantictoken":{"identifier":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/oudstokenssemantic\/elevationcompositesemantictoken","titleInlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ElevationCompositeSemanticToken"}],"type":"link","title":"ElevationCompositeSemanticToken","url":"https:\/\/ios.unified-design-system.orange.com\/documentation\/oudstokenssemantic\/elevationcompositesemantictoken"}}}